commit.message:
locale_facets_nonio.h (time_get::get_time): Doc typo.

2010-10-05  Jonathan Wakely  <jwakely.gcc@gmail.com>

	* include/bits/locale_facets_nonio.h (time_get::get_time): Doc typo.
